==Quotations==
*"I<U+2019>m told that when [[W. H. Auden|Auden]] died, they found his Oxford [English Dictionary] all but clawed to pieces. That is the way a [[poet]] and his [[dictionary]] should come out."<ref>{{cite web | title=''Simpson<U+2019>s Contemporary Quotations,'' No.7532 | url=http://www.bartleby.com/63/32/7532.html | author=Francis Steegmuller | work=New York Times, 26 March 1980 | accessdate=2007-01-29}}</ref>

